<html><head></head><body dir=3D"auto" style=3D"overflow-wrap: =
break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; line-break: =
after-white-space;"><div>Kia ora team,</div><div><br></div><div>Thank =
you for your email.</div><div><br></div><div>I=E2=80=99d like to clarify =
a few points so we can bring this to a timely =
conclusion:</div><div><br></div><div><b>Timeframes</b></div><div>My =
Privacy Act request was made on 1 July 2025. The statutory timeframe has =
passed. On 15 September 2025 I was told the additional material would be =
provided within 5 working days. Could you please explain why the date =
has now moved to 8 October, and on what =
basis?</div><div><br></div><div><b>Privacy &amp; =
security</b></div><div>There have been several issues to date (broken =
ShareFile links, visibility of another customer=E2=80=99s folder, and =
access not tied to my identity). I appreciate that you have notified OPC =
and recreated folders; however, these incidents, combined with delay, =
have caused avoidable stress. Please confirm the containment steps taken =
and that all records relevant to both claims are being =
preserved.</div><div><br></div><div><b>Redactions</b></div><div>The =
material provided so far is heavily redacted without identification of =
the grounds relied upon. For every redaction or withholding, please set =
out the specific ground and provide the least-redacted version =
possible.</div><div><br></div><div><b>Fees</b></div><div>I do not accept =
that a fee is appropriate in this case. No charges were mentioned =
previously, and it is Tower=E2=80=99s responsibility to maintain and =
retrieve my claim information. If you now believe a fee is required, =
please set out:</div><div><br></div><div><ul class=3D"MailOutline"><li>the=
 legal basis you rely on,</li><li>the specific activities the fee would =
cover, and</li><li>the total amount, and how this is &nbsp;calculated =
and why you believe it is =
&nbsp;reasonable</li></ul></div><div><br></div><div><b>Delivery</b></div><=
div>Please confirm that the complete files for both claims=E2=80=94togethe=
r with an index and the specific grounds for any redactions=E2=80=94will =
be provided by 8 October 2025, without further extension and without =
charge.</div><div><br></div><div>I remain keen to resolve this directly. =
If it cannot be resolved on this basis, I will consider referring the =
matter to the Office of the Privacy =
Commissioner</div><div><br></div><div>Ng=C4=81 mihi,</div><div>Raffaella =
